<h1 class="display-4 text-center border-bottom">Numerical Mathematics - Overview</h1>

<p>Numerical mathematics, also known as Numerics, is a branch of mathematics that constructs and analyzes algorithms for continuous mathematical problems. The main application is the approximate calculation of solutions through approximation algorithms using computers.</p>

<p>On this website you can find modules which visualize numerical algorithms.</p>

